sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant V as harness-verify
    participant M as context-memory<br/>Post-Ship Sync
    participant I as INDEX.md
    participant A as Feature Artifacts
    participant F as Memory Files
    participant E as session-extracts.md
    participant S as status.md

    V->>V: Mechanical gate + Alignment + Security PASS
    V->>M: Hand off to Post-Ship Sync
    M->>I: Read listed memory files (create INDEX.md if missing)
    I-->>M: Always + By-Intent + By-Debug groups
    M->>A: Read feature artifacts (spec, plan, review, ADRs)
    A-->>M: Durable changes and logs
    loop For each file in INDEX.md
        M->>F: Read memory file
        alt Durable change found
            M->>F: Apply diff (Update)
            M->>M: Check promotion threshold (lines/subtopics/refs)
            alt Threshold crossed
                M->>I: Add to ## Promotion Watchlist
                M->>A: Write promotions.md proposal
            end
        else No change needed
            M->>M: Formulate 1-line reason untouched
        end
    end
    M->>E: Write compiled sweep record to ## Post-Ship Sync block
    M->>M: Verify every INDEX.md file appears once in record
    alt Sweep verification passes
        M-->>V: OK — sync record complete
        V->>S: Set phase = Done
    else Generic skip or gaps found
        M-->>V: REJECT — fails verification gate
    end

    Note over V,F: Profile gating:<br/>Tiny = heuristic-only sweep<br/>Standard+ = full sweep
